{"tid":815552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經睇到山竹黎緊一星期嘅命運","createTime":"2018-09-12T06:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T07:15:56.000Z","uid":35776,"like":18,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"601073e77e7b93f9cf47d5a9fadfce3948598afb","tid":815552,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"hi 到呂宋已經廢一半武功<br />\n前面仲有個風預早吸走南海熱量<br />\n連重新發展都唔得 最後係香港以南三百公里左右路過<br />\n預早半個星期煞有介事做準備<br />\n結果得個強三驚會冇面<br />\n所以大交合頂盡開個弱八當交差<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(一係強三一係弱八)</span><br />\n之後又繼續吹香港係福地<br />\n<br />\n結果早已預訂<br />\n學生哥學生妹好好享受弱八風假<br />\n手停口停繼續手停口停<br />\n無災無難有雨無水浸<br />\n鳩鐵繼續鳩下鳩下未爆住<br />\n<br />\n最多有傻仔玩水/行山蕩失路call飛行服務隊<br />\n然後又入個風數 講幾日打風都行山唔值得救云云 奶共網媒再老吹行山人士係港獨or黃絲點樣無腦 blablabla<br />\n<br />\n結論係打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(香港大眾想點實際就掉番轉 事與願違呢點就成日中)<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2e840120a681a98e41d694fce7bbc00135de32","tid":815552,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b71f94027ac598e1518af3a2adbee764f5194d","tid":815552,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"每年風季都對社會造成嚴重撕裂<br />\n山竹踩緊中央政府嘅紅線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86f8ec0da7883b281f037bac4ba9abb286991a8","tid":815552,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗一日又話香港係褔地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975eac633502c05a9712df0fd5a7996b943e17b4","tid":815552,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"原